data.description: Listed Well Below Market Value! Property needs some cosmetic updating such as Paint & Carpet, etc. Comparable properties in the area are selling in the mid 500s! Huge opportunity for someone who is looking for instant equity! Escape to your serene countryside haven! This 6 acre property features a horse barn, a 30x50 spacious workshop with 2 horse stalls, and a large fenced backyard that includes an underground storm shelter. This cozy home offers a spacious kitchen, a large area for entertaining, a 3 car garage, and a peaceful primary suite. Enjoy the quiet and tranquil surroundings, away from the hustle and bustle. Embrace the perfect blend of comfort and functionality – make this your dream retreat today! This one will not last long! NO HOA!
